[Episode 22]

13
00:01:02,430 --> 00:01:03,320
Chairman Ye,

14
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,200
suddenly, there are

15
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,350
overwhelming reports online

16
00:01:05,350 --> 00:01:07,230
claiming that Ye Group's
capital chain is broken.

17
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:09,000
Now the company's stock price
is plummeting.

18
00:01:09,310 --> 00:01:10,950
Chairman Ye, you must
give us an explanation.

19
00:01:11,150 --> 00:01:12,070
There are also rumors

20
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:13,870
that you and your daughter
are counting assets

21
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:14,840
to prepare for a sell-off.

22
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:15,870
Is this true?

23
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,560
Enough.

24
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:21,840
I'm right here. Where will I escape?

25
00:01:22,310 --> 00:01:24,070
But why has Miss Ye
been absent for so long?

26
00:01:24,070 --> 00:01:25,150
Where exactly is she hiding?

27
00:01:26,430 --> 00:01:27,430
Yes, where is she?

28
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:28,560
Does she need to explain

29
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,920
her whereabouts to you?

30
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,680
- There's Miss Ye.
- I'm Ye Xiyan, CEO of Ye Group.

31
00:01:39,230 --> 00:01:40,920
As for the recent rumors,

32
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,710
they're malicious fabrications
by ill-intentioned people.

33
00:01:44,230 --> 00:01:45,230
Ye Group

34
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:47,310
has indeed encountered
some difficulties,

35
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:49,400
but they aren't as exaggerated
as the rumors claim.

36
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:51,840
I promise I won't escape.

37
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,710
I'll take all responsibilities

38
00:01:53,710 --> 00:01:55,150
and give you a satisfactory explanation.

39
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:02,640
A brilliant speech.

40
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:05,120
You're indeed the woman I love.

41
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,310
What are you doing here?

42
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,560
Isn't it enough to hide in the shadows
and watch the show?

43
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,910
You have to come here in person.

44
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:14,150
Don't be so arrogant.

45
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,750
Right now, I'm the only one
who can help you.

46
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:22,310
If harm counts as help,

47
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,360
then yes, you've helped me.

48
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,430
Thank you

49
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:27,710
for toughening my heart.

50
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:32,560
Xiyan,

51
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:35,630
you should already know

52
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:39,430
the financial crisis of Ye Group

53
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:41,680
can't be solved overnight.

54
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,080
Without the support of a large group

55
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,710
and enough positive news,

56
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,630
it's hard to turn the situation around.

57
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,910
What exactly are you trying to say?

58
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,150
I'm giving you two choices.

59
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:02,840
First,

60
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,000
marry me

61
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,360
and merge Ye Group with Cui Group.

62
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,960
We'll join forces

63
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:12,800
to develop the tea plantation.

64
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,800
Second,

65
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:22,310
Cui Group will take advantage
of this opportunity

66
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:25,560
to buy Ye Group's shares at a low price,

67
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:29,150
and Ye Group
will be devoured completely.

68
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,190
Naturally,

69
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,910
the tea leaves of Guyan Village

70
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,310
will also face devastating damage.

71
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,360
Despicable!

72
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,560
You're delusional.

73
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,520
Think it over.

74
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,910
I'll wait for the day
you come begging me.

75
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,720
For me?

76
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:59,420
[Business License]

77
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:02,460
[Motor Vehicle Registration Certificate]

78
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:03,660
[Real Estate Certificate]

79
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,830
These are all of my personal assets.

80
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,000
You can use them as you need.

81
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,270
Although

82
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,070
it won't solve all the problems,

83
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,920
it can alleviate the urgent ones.

84
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:23,560
Your presence has made me realize

85
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:27,310
my imagination of a good man
isn't rich enough.

86
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,830
Don't worry.

87
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:33,630
Every difficulty will be overcome.

88
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:34,950
I'll be with you through it all.

89
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:38,860
♪There will be banks on the way♪

90
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,600
Then come with me to a place.

91
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,240
There's something
I've always wanted to do.

92
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:50,500
♪I want to become the scenery
that always accompanies you♪

93
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:56,740
♪With you, I fearlessly cross mountains♪

94
00:05:58,340 --> 00:06:01,460
♪Now I will run towards you again♪

95
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:02,560
Do we hang it on the tree?

96
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,630
Hanging it on the tree is so tacky.

97
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:09,000
Let's bury it.

98
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:11,660
♪Longing makes it fall to the ground♪

99
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:14,460
♪If I still fail to reunite with you
the next century♪

100
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:18,460
♪Then I'll wait through
more stormy seasons♪

101
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:23,580
♪Every breath, after evaporating
