00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:28,300
♪In the quest to travel the world♪

103
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:45,220
♪Perhaps frozen in winter♪

104
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:48,700
♪There will be banks on the way♪

105
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,600
It seems someone

106
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,600
had the same idea as us.

107
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,190
I just don't know

108
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,510
what their experiences were like.

109
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:02,190
Was the ending happy or sad?

110
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,830
Looks like

111
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,120
it's been here for a century.

112
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,750
Love in the Republic of China era

113
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,430
was often tragic.

114
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:18,700
♪Love won't disappear like clouds♪

115
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:21,060
♪Longing makes it fall to the ground♪

116
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,920
Lovers were unable to stay together.

117
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:24,700
[Marriage]

118
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,830
I used to not understand

119
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:30,190
why people who loved each other
would eventually part.

120
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:33,680
Now I think I understand a bit.

121
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:38,220
♪In the quest to travel the world♪

122
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,190
What's wrong with you?

123
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:54,160
Look, a shooting star.

124
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:57,750
Quickly, close your eyes
and make a wish.

125
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,950
Xiyan,

126
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,000
have you really decided

127
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:08,600
to accept Cui Zihao's terms?

128
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,310
Yes.

129
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,560
I can't watch

130
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,390
Ye Group collapse.

131
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:21,270
I also don't want Guyan Village
to be implicated

132
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:23,800
and Mingyu's hard work destroyed.

133
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:27,390
Then you and Mingyu...

134
00:08:32,790 --> 00:08:35,630
We might be

135
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:36,960
lovers who are destined

136
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,600
but can't stay together.

137
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:42,630
I'm sorry, Mingyu.

138
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,510
I love you,

139
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:46,840
but I can't continue to love you.

140
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:50,200
Everyone has their own responsibilities.

141
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,510
I hope you can

142
