157
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,000
Alright.

158
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:11,840
Miss Ye,

159
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,910
according to your instructions,

160
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:15,320
