163
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,120
Xiyan,

164
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,270
don't go.

165
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:48,820
♪You're like a spontaneous journey♪

166
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:51,820
♪You're like an unfinished movie♪

167
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:54,080
Share your troubles with me.

168
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,440
