♪You're like a spontaneous journey♪

178
00:12:33,580 --> 00:12:36,940
♪You're like an unfinished movie♪

179
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:40,540
♪You took away all the air around me♪

180
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:44,140
♪I can't move or make a sound♪

181
00:12:44,660 --> 00:12:47,860
♪You brought me
this earth-shattering love♪

182
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:51,980
♪I love you far more than you imagine♪

183
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:58,500
♪Small emotions, once cared for,
become meaningful♪

184
00:13:05,690 --> 00:13:08,450
♪I open my eyes and see you,
my heart suddenly becomes full♪

185
00:13:09,050 --> 00:13:11,970
♪Every stroke of the word
becomes clearer bit by bit♪

186
00:13:12,410 --> 00:13:15,490
♪After 300 thousand time units,
wishes ignite shooting stars♪

187
00:13:15,930 --> 00:13:19,090
♪When cherry blossom petals fall,
they travel much more than 5cm♪

188
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:22,370
♪Planets attract each other,
bringing us closer together♪

189
00:13:22,730 --> 00:13:25,970
♪Love is like a lighter,
a touch creates an echo♪

190
00:13:26,490 --> 00:13:29,010
♪I've also walked alone
through lost dreams♪

191
00:13:29,450 --> 00:13:31,810
♪Finally awakening because of you♪

192
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:35,810
♪As swift as a monsoon,
you suddenly appear♪

193
00:13:36,090 --> 00:13:39,330
♪Raindrops from across the sea
give me all the courage♪

194
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:42,530
♪Kissing your eyes
as our shoulders meet♪

195
00:13:42,810 --> 00:13:45,970
♪My traces are in your starry sky♪

196
00:13:46,170 --> 00:13:49,650
♪Like the night sky summoning
shooting stars, you descend for me♪

197
00:13:50,010 --> 00:13:53,090
♪Standing at the world's center,
I hold your hand in mine♪

198
00:13:53,450 --> 00:13:56,690
♪The sound of heartbeats hitting walls♪

199
00:13:57,050 --> 00:14:02,450
